    "en": {
      "title": "Announcement of school holidays",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Bandula Gunawardena has announced that schools located in the Colombo Zone, suburbs of the Western Province and major cities in all provinces will be closed until July 10.",
        "He said schools in other areas would act in accordance with the decision of the principals and education authorities."
      ],
